---
layout: base.njk
title: Koncerty
description: Seznam všech koncertů komorního orchestru
permalink: /koncerty/
---

<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold mb-12 text-center">Koncerty</h1>
    
    {% set concerts = collections.concerts | sortByDate %}
    {% if concerts | length > 0 %}
    <div class="space-y-8">
      {% for concert in concerts %}
      <article class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
        <div class="p-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-4">
            <div class="mb-4 md:mb-0">
              <div class="text-sm text-primary-600 font-semibold mb-2">
                {{ concert.data.date | dateFormat }}
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold mb-2">
                <a href="{{ concert.url }}" class="hover:text-primary-600 transition-colors">
                  {{ concert.data.title }}
                </a>
              </h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 inline-block mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                </svg>
                {{ concert.data.place }}
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <a href="{{ concert.url }}" class="btn btn-primary text-center">
                Více informací
              </a>
              {% if concert.data.invitation %}
              <a href="{{ concert.data.invitation }}" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary text-center">
                Pozvánka (PDF)
              </a>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </div>
          
          {% if concert.data.description %}
          <div class="prose max-w-none mt-4">
            {{ concert.data.description | markdown | safe }}
          </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="text-center py-16">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-4">Momentálně nemáme naplánované žádné koncerty.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Sledujte nás pro aktualizace o nadcházejících vystoupeních.</p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>

